# Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
# files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.

## Build results
bin/
obj/

## User-specific files
*.user
*.userosscache
*.suo
*.userprefs

## Mono auto-generated files
mono_crash.*

## Visual Studio Code files
.vscode/

## Rider IDE files
.idea/

## DotNet CLI Tools
*.dotCover
*.ncrunch*
*.VisualState.xml
*.vspscc
*.vssscc

## ASP.NET Core Secrets
secrets.json

## Publish output folder
publish/
publish_output/

## Backup & temporary files
*.bak
*.backup
*.tmp
*.temp

## Log files
*.log

## NuGet packages
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
packages/
.nuget/

## ASP.NET Scaffolding
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

## Microsoft Azure Web App publish settings
*.PublishSettings

## IIS Express
/IISExpress/

## JetBrains Rider
.idea/

## DotCover coverage reports
*.dotCover

## Others
*.dbmdl
*.pdb
*.cache
*.pidb
*.svclog

## Resharper
_ReSharper*/

## StyleCop
StyleCopReport.xml

## Docker
docker-compose.override.yml

## Test results
TestResults/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## Others
*.vs/
.vs/

## Entity Framework Core Migrations
**/Migrations/*.Designer.cs
**/Migrations/*.resx

